    "Details": "<color=#F79B26>The Hammer is a light 'Mech that was built to provide fire support to other 'Mechs with its long-range arsenal. It is often paired with the Anvil, softening up the enemy at a distance until the Anvil can bring its lasers to bear.</color>\n\nThe 3S, commonly called the Slammer, aims to increase the longevity of the Hammer on the battlefield as a fire support 'Mech. This is done by removing two of the Medium Lasers and replacing them with two more tons of ammunition. The 'Mech can subsequently fire a sustained barrage of LRM fire for up to eight minutes.",
